29
00:03:06,636 --> 00:03:09,685
Is there any special reason for you to stop me from doing that?

30
00:03:24,521 --> 00:03:26,035
What's this?

31
00:03:27,891 --> 00:03:29,375
What?

32
00:03:34,197 --> 00:03:36,685
(Jung Su Ah)

33
00:03:37,467 --> 00:03:39,155
This photo...

34
00:03:40,437 --> 00:03:42,400
(Jung Su Ah)

35
00:03:42,405 --> 00:03:44,025
Jung Su Ah?

36
00:04:03,293 --> 00:04:05,145
Unbelievable.

37
00:04:05,428 --> 00:04:08,290
I hit the jackpot.

38
00:04:08,298 --> 00:04:10,685
(Jung Su Ah)

39
00:04:11,067 --> 00:04:13,585
What's happening?

40
00:04:28,285 --> 00:04:30,375
Jackpot.

41
00:04:30,987 --> 00:04:33,535
Don't disconnect yet.

42
00:04:38,161 --> 00:04:40,090
Why are you standing up? Stay seated.

43
00:04:40,096 --> 00:04:41,730
I don't know what's with you.

44
00:04:41,731 --> 00:04:44,155
