45
00:04:44,968 --> 00:04:48,230
Mr. Gi, just give him his phone. It's distracting.

46
00:04:48,238 --> 00:04:51,440
- Seriously. - What is this?

47
00:04:51,441 --> 00:04:53,270
- Just let him go out. - I can't focus.

48
00:04:53,276 --> 00:04:55,465
It's so distracting.

49
00:04:56,346 --> 00:04:58,335
Darn it.

50
00:05:00,083 --> 00:05:02,435
I'll submit my answer sheet anyway.

51
00:05:10,627 --> 00:05:12,175
Didn't you hear me?

52
00:05:14,297 --> 00:05:16,285
Stay seated.

53
00:05:17,267 --> 00:05:18,760
That's strange.

54
00:05:18,768 --> 00:05:21,630
You always make a point of sticking to the rules.

55
00:05:21,638 --> 00:05:24,755
And why are you being so unreasonable now?

56
00:05:25,275 --> 00:05:26,910
Suit yourself.

57
00:05:26,910 --> 00:05:29,295
I'll just do what the rules say.

58
00:05:36,353 --> 00:05:39,435
Let me check my phone in front of you and return it.

59
00:05:39,823 --> 00:05:41,805
That's no problem, right?

60
00:06:05,148 --> 00:06:06,980
Oh, come on!

61
00:06:06,983 --> 00:06:08,880
- My phone's brand new! - Darn it.

62
00:06:08,885 --> 00:06:11,380
- Give us more time for the test! - My phone.

63
00:06:11,388 --> 00:06:13,905
I'm going to submit a complaint.

64
00:06:14,391 --> 00:06:17,920
Sorry. I'll give you more time. Sorry.

65
00:06:17,927 --> 00:06:20,045
Here it is. Yu Beom Jin.

66
00:06:21,731 --> 00:06:23,185
Here.

67
00:06:25,902 --> 00:06:28,625
What? You kept asking for it.

68
00:06:35,178 --> 00:06:36,825
