71
00:06:48,725 --> 00:06:50,275
How could this be?

72
00:06:52,595 --> 00:06:56,145
Well, maybe there's something wrong with the battery.

73
00:06:57,233 --> 00:07:00,370
Maybe. I probably should have it checked.

74
00:07:00,370 --> 00:07:02,555
To see if it's really a battery problem...

75
00:07:03,206 --> 00:07:05,095
or if it's something else.

76
00:07:15,552 --> 00:07:17,175
Gosh!

77
00:07:17,554 --> 00:07:19,605
I said not to disconnect!

78
00:07:25,195 --> 00:07:26,945
Good job.

79
00:07:28,598 --> 00:07:30,385
You did a good job.

80
