82
00:07:49,552 --> 00:07:52,005
Good job.

83
00:07:53,122 --> 00:07:54,645
Well done.

84
00:08:04,434 --> 00:08:06,060
- Hey. - Hey!

85
00:08:06,069 --> 00:08:08,700
