96
00:08:31,394 --> 00:08:33,760
We're supposed to put them in the safe right away.

97
00:08:33,763 --> 00:08:36,215
Right. I'm on my way to the teacher's office.

98
00:08:36,533 --> 00:08:38,830
- Let's go. - Okay, let's go.

99
00:08:38,835 --> 00:08:41,085
- Please. - All right.

100
