106
00:09:17,373 --> 00:09:20,610
Instead of a rat who digs around for others' secrets.

107
00:09:20,610 --> 00:09:22,740
What? A rat?

108
00:09:22,745 --> 00:09:25,995
A general manager...

109
00:09:26,182 --> 00:09:28,305
has more work than you think.

110
00:09:30,019 --> 00:09:31,875
Even more than a director.

111
00:09:32,021 --> 00:09:34,045
So please work hard.

112
00:09:35,425 --> 00:09:36,905
Brother.

113
00:09:38,528 --> 00:09:40,360
Know your place.

114
00:09:40,363 --> 00:09:43,215
Who do you think you are?

115
00:09:46,769 --> 00:09:50,340
Father, please wait just a little longer.

116
00:09:50,340 --> 00:09:52,070
I'll make sure you get to see...

117
00:09:52,075 --> 00:09:55,910
Woonam University in Cheonmyung Foundation's organization chart...

118
00:09:55,912 --> 00:09:58,065
during your life.

119
00:10:16,265 --> 00:10:21,900
Father, please stay healthy

120
00:10:21,904 --> 00:10:25,395
Gosh, why is that idiot so stuck-up?

121
00:10:29,012 --> 00:10:30,465
What?

122
00:10:40,690 --> 00:10:42,405
This is Lee Tae Seok.

123
00:10:49,732 --> 00:10:52,255
Yes. Thank you.

124
00:10:52,268 --> 00:10:54,655
I'll come to you right now.

125
00:10:55,238 --> 00:10:56,685
Okay.

126
00:10:57,373 --> 00:10:59,525
Yes!

127
00:11:00,910 --> 00:11:02,470
A spy app?

128
00:11:02,478 --> 00:11:05,040
Why would a high school student have a spy app on his phone?

129
00:11:05,048 --> 00:11:07,535
That's why it's a jackpot.

130
00:11:08,217 --> 00:11:09,810
Daily Weather.

131
00:11:09,819 --> 00:11:13,105
At a glance, it looks like an ordinary weather app.

132
00:11:15,491 --> 00:11:18,420
But if you install this app on two phones,

133
00:11:18,428 --> 00:11:22,690
you can monitor and access the messages, photos,

134
00:11:22,699 --> 00:11:26,830
and internet browsing history on one phone from the other.

135
00:11:26,836 --> 00:11:30,955
In other words, this app can do both hacking and monitoring.

136
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:33,910
Monitoring? But monitor who?

137
00:11:33,910 --> 00:11:36,570
Exactly. That's the part we want to know.

138
00:11:36,579 --> 00:11:39,180
Because you disconnected the phones in the middle of the process,

139
00:11:39,182 --> 00:11:41,335
all the data got damaged.

140
00:11:42,051 --> 00:11:44,105
I barely managed to save this one photo.

141
00:11:48,424 --> 00:11:51,345
That's why he kept asking me to return his phone.

142
00:11:51,394 --> 00:11:54,260
(Jung Su Ah)

143
00:11:54,263 --> 00:11:57,060
Can you try to connect again?

144
00:11:57,066 --> 00:11:59,385
No. That's too dangerous.

145
00:12:00,703 --> 00:12:02,655
Anyway, we know one thing for sure.

146
00:12:03,139 --> 00:12:07,595
That person has Jung Su Ah's profile pictures on his phone.

147
00:12:08,544 --> 00:12:12,035
Lee Tae Seok. That makes sense.

148
00:12:12,782 --> 00:12:16,105
But why would Yu Beom Jin want to monitor him?

149
00:12:16,486 --> 00:12:18,705
What's their relation?

150
00:12:20,356 --> 00:12:23,650
While Gi Hoon's phone surprisingly turned out to have nothing,

151
00:12:23,659 --> 00:12:27,485
this gem just popped out from somewhere completely unexpected.

152
00:12:27,697 --> 00:12:29,690
On Byung Ho's phone,

153
00:12:29,699 --> 00:12:33,630
we found his messages with Lee Tae Seok, so that's not bad.

154
00:12:33,636 --> 00:12:35,785
(Yu Beom Jin, Congressman Yu Yang Ki's son)

155
00:12:37,306 --> 00:12:38,940
- Won Suk. - Yes?

156
00:12:38,941 --> 00:12:42,210
Which standing committees does Yu Yang Ki belong too?

157
00:12:42,211 --> 00:12:43,665
Hold on a second.

158
00:12:44,680 --> 00:12:45,840
Let me see.

159
00:12:45,848 --> 00:12:49,035
(Yu Yang Ki)

160
00:12:49,051 --> 00:12:50,720
Legislation and Judiciary Committee.

161
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:52,620
National Defense Committee. Culture, Sports, and Tourism Committee.

162
00:12:52,622 --> 00:12:54,245
And Education Committee.

163
00:12:55,358 --> 00:12:57,075
He is the chairman of Education Committee.

164
00:12:59,195 --> 00:13:01,215
(Yu Yang Ki)

165
00:13:03,466 --> 00:13:04,700
Then he could play an important role...

166
00:13:04,700 --> 00:13:09,225
in Lee Tae Seok taking over Woonam University.

167
00:13:09,372 --> 00:13:12,795
What if Yu Yang Ki, not Lee Do Jin,

168
00:13:14,243 --> 00:13:16,595
is Speed Dial Zero?

169
00:13:16,946 --> 00:13:18,895
He might be the one...

170
00:13:20,216 --> 00:13:22,005
who has pictures of Su Ah on his phone.

171
00:13:23,619 --> 00:13:24,880
No way.

172
00:13:24,887 --> 00:13:27,990
We must recover the data from Yu Beom Jin's phone.

173
00:13:27,990 --> 00:13:30,945
That will reveal who Yu Beom Jin...

174
00:13:33,663 --> 00:13:35,785
has been monitoring.

175
00:13:39,635 --> 00:13:42,885
(Congressman Yu Yang Ki)

176
00:13:57,486 --> 00:13:58,950
Here it is. Yu Beom Jin.

177
00:13:58,955 --> 00:14:00,705
(Yu Beom Jin)

178
00:14:01,224 --> 00:14:02,705
Here.

179
00:14:05,094 --> 00:14:07,190
What? You kept asking for it.

180
00:14:07,196 --> 00:14:08,915
(Yu Beom Jin)

181
00:14:17,306 --> 00:14:18,755
Beom Jin.

182
00:14:19,175 --> 00:14:20,470
Why are you concentrating so hard?

183
00:14:20,476 --> 00:14:22,995
You'll be the top student anyway.

184
00:14:26,148 --> 00:14:29,010
By the way, are you okay?

185
00:14:29,018 --> 00:14:30,780
What? What do you mean?

186
00:14:30,786 --> 00:14:34,575
Have you found Ms. Jo's replacement?

187
00:14:35,625 --> 00:14:39,475
Yes, my mom hired a new teacher.

188
00:14:39,528 --> 00:14:40,560
Who?

189
00:14:40,563 --> 00:14:44,185
Who else? Our new homeroom teacher.

190
00:14:48,271 --> 00:14:49,770
Why don't you find another one?

191
00:14:49,772 --> 00:14:51,670
He keeps digging into the past.

192
00:14:51,674 --> 00:14:53,855
He's unreasonably curious.

193
00:14:54,610 --> 00:14:56,465
You must feel uncomfortable yourself...

194
00:14:57,446 --> 00:15:01,305
leaving your future in that suspicious person's hands.

195
00:15:01,817 --> 00:15:05,535
I have no choice. It's Mom's decision.

196
00:15:06,989 --> 00:15:09,020
Why did Mom have to choose the temp?

197
00:15:09,025 --> 00:15:11,690
I'm sure he was chosen by Butler Lee, not your mom,

198
00:15:11,694 --> 00:15:13,875
because the temp suits his purpose.

199
00:15:14,363 --> 00:15:15,915
His purpose?

200
00:15:16,766 --> 00:15:18,385
What's that?

201
00:15:33,115 --> 00:15:36,705
Yu Yang Ki's son had that photo on his phone.

202
00:15:36,719 --> 00:15:38,275
Congressman Yu Yang Ki's son?

203
00:15:38,554 --> 00:15:40,480
How did you find that out?

204
00:15:40,489 --> 00:15:43,590
I hacked a few suspicious kids' phones.

205
00:15:43,592 --> 00:15:45,920
There were some opportunities during the exams.

206
00:15:45,928 --> 00:15:46,920
Mu Hyeok.

207
00:15:46,929 --> 00:15:49,485
That's not the point.

208
00:15:52,335 --> 00:15:56,000
Yu Yang Ki is the chairman of Education Committee.

209
00:15:56,005 --> 00:15:59,925
He might have a relation with Lee Tae Seok.

210
00:16:02,979 --> 00:16:05,140
In addition to Assistant Prosecutor General Yang and Lee Do Jin,

211
00:16:05,147 --> 00:16:06,935
now a congressman?

212
00:16:09,819 --> 00:16:11,375
How is the investigation going?

213
00:16:11,921 --> 00:16:14,720
All investigations on Lee Tae Seok are on hold.

214
00:16:14,724 --> 00:16:17,090
The circumstances clearly point to Kim Han Su.

215
00:16:17,093 --> 00:16:19,260
There's absolutely no chance for a reinvestigation.

216
00:16:19,261 --> 00:16:21,545
He was not only arrested at the scene...

217
00:16:21,764 --> 00:16:26,215
but also caught on security cameras rushing into her apartment.

218
00:16:26,602 --> 00:16:28,185
Security cameras...

219
00:16:28,938 --> 00:16:30,785
Did you check the whole neighborhood?

220
00:16:31,707 --> 00:16:35,565
No other outsiders entered that building around that time.

221
00:16:36,245 --> 00:16:38,910
You should focus on interrogating Assistant Prosecutor General Yang.

222
00:16:38,914 --> 00:16:42,005
I'll try to find the evidence needed for a reinvestigation.

223
00:16:46,722 --> 00:16:49,620
(Namgang Office)

224
00:16:49,625 --> 00:16:52,945
We must work together...

225
00:16:53,095 --> 00:16:55,790
to never let our children...

226
00:16:55,798 --> 00:17:00,100
be sacrificed by excessive private education again.

227
00:17:00,102 --> 00:17:02,500
We're going to cooperate with Seoul Metropolitan Office of Education...

228
00:17:02,505 --> 00:17:04,770
and investigate every private academy...

229
00:17:04,774 --> 00:17:06,570
in our district...

230
00:17:06,575 --> 00:17:09,440
and carry out random checks at night.

231
00:17:09,445 --> 00:17:11,880
Sir, I have a question.

232
00:17:11,881 --> 00:17:14,810
After his speech, please.

233
00:17:14,817 --> 00:17:17,875
It's okay. Please go ahead.

234
00:17:18,788 --> 00:17:20,680
I'm Reporter Han Da Hee from Education Journal.

235
00:17:20,689 --> 00:17:21,750
Considering the Namgang-gu citizen's...

236
00:17:21,757 --> 00:17:24,090
great zeal for education,

237
00:17:24,093 --> 00:17:27,090
such a move can be seen as pressure on private education,

238
00:17:27,096 --> 00:17:30,460
which will highly likely to lead to the drop of your approval ratings.

239
00:17:30,466 --> 00:17:32,830
What do you think about this?

240
00:17:32,835 --> 00:17:35,970
Are you saying sticking to the rules and normal operation of academies...

241
00:17:35,971 --> 00:17:38,700
are pressure on private education?

242
00:17:38,707 --> 00:17:40,070
Of course not.

243
00:17:40,076 --> 00:17:43,370
But parents who send their children to the academies...

244
00:17:43,379 --> 00:17:44,640
might have different opinions.

245
00:17:44,647 --> 00:17:47,240
Are you saying the people can't understand...

246
00:17:47,249 --> 00:17:51,005
what you and I think is normal?

247
00:17:53,355 --> 00:17:55,790
I believe our people...

248
00:17:55,791 --> 00:17:58,460
are insightful enough...

249
00:17:58,461 --> 00:18:01,945
to make wise choices and decisions.

250
00:18:04,800 --> 00:18:07,160
All academies that are caught during the investigation...

251
00:18:07,169 --> 00:18:08,830
will be disqualified as an educational institution...

252
00:18:08,838 --> 00:18:13,225
without exception. I give you my word.

253
00:18:14,276 --> 00:18:17,410
I would like to ask you all a favor.

254
00:18:17,413 --> 00:18:20,880
The education office and we are working together.

255
00:18:20,883 --> 00:18:24,875
Please think of this matter as your own children's.

256
00:18:25,254 --> 00:18:28,445
Your cooperation will be very much appreciated.

257
00:18:44,874 --> 00:18:48,610
So this is the only entrance to the townhouse, right?

258
00:18:48,611 --> 00:18:50,995
Yes, there's no other entrance.

259
00:19:52,808 --> 00:19:55,910
Are those all the cameras that film the back of the building?

260
00:19:55,911 --> 00:19:58,395
Yes, those are all.

261
00:20:02,618 --> 00:20:04,135
(Pause, lap)

262
00:20:43,292 --> 00:20:45,675
1 minute and 20 seconds.

263
00:20:46,662 --> 00:20:48,915
It's so close.

264
00:20:56,905 --> 00:20:59,570
What's the matter? What about this place?

265
00:20:59,575 --> 00:21:03,240
I found another way to Su Ah's place.

266
00:21:03,245 --> 00:21:04,835
Another way?

267
00:21:06,782 --> 00:21:08,510
If you cut across here, it takes less than two minutes...

268
00:21:08,517 --> 00:21:10,280
to Su Ah's place.

269
00:21:10,286 --> 00:21:12,605
The police must have missed it.

270
