01:01:18,591 --> 01:01:19,890
Now that you know,

818
01:01:19,893 --> 01:01:23,120
shut your mouth and go to school diligently.

819
01:01:23,129 --> 01:01:25,190
Darn it. Mr. Lee...

820
01:01:25,198 --> 01:01:29,415
couldn't keep his son under control and created this mess.

821
01:01:29,502 --> 01:01:31,685
Why you!

822
01:01:40,346 --> 01:01:41,880
Darn it.

823
01:01:41,881 --> 01:01:42,940
You jerk.

824
01:01:42,949 --> 01:01:48,835
Die.

825
01:01:50,023 --> 01:01:52,590
You brat. You have no respect for your elders.

826
01:01:52,592 --> 01:01:54,620
What? Butler Lee?

827
01:01:54,627 --> 01:01:56,890
Did you think I didn't know, you punk?

828
01:01:56,896 --> 01:02:01,085
Die.

829
01:02:04,571 --> 01:02:06,485
Get over here, punk.

830
01:02:09,109 --> 01:02:11,310
If it weren't for your father...

831
01:02:11,311 --> 01:02:12,710
You're a lucky punk.

832
01:02:12,712 --> 01:02:16,135
You lucked out with good parents, you rude punk.

833
01:02:18,218 --> 01:02:21,180
Hey. Scram. Got it?

834
01:02:21,187 --> 01:02:25,390
If you barge in here again, I'll really kill you. Got that?

835
01:02:25,391 --> 01:02:27,645
You punk.

836
01:02:30,396 --> 01:02:32,185
You punk.

837
01:02:48,148 --> 01:02:49,895
I don't want to go to work.

838
01:02:50,350 --> 01:02:51,810
I wish...

839
01:02:51,818 --> 01:02:53,920
when I wake up tomorrow, the school would've exploded.

840
01:02:53,920 --> 01:02:56,180
I agree with you.

841
01:02:56,189 --> 01:02:59,590
It was sweet because it was exam time.

842
01:02:59,592 --> 01:03:01,460
The students will flood into the office starting tomorrow...

843
01:03:01,461 --> 01:03:02,860
to complain.

844
01:03:02,862 --> 01:03:06,845
"Why is this answer wrong? Maybe there are two right answers."

845
01:03:07,300 --> 01:03:10,925
They get their test papers checked by college professors.

846
01:03:11,037 --> 01:03:13,430
Then why do they ask us to submit the questions?

847
01:03:13,439 --> 01:03:16,355
They should just get them from a professor.

848
01:03:16,976 --> 01:03:18,910
Okay, let's drink.

849
01:03:18,912 --> 01:03:20,425
Let's drink.

850
01:03:26,619 --> 01:03:28,980
What is wrong with you?

851
01:03:28,988 --> 01:03:30,950
We finally get to hang out now that exams are over,

852
01:03:30,957 --> 01:03:33,375
but you're silent like you're in mourning.

853
01:03:33,560 --> 01:03:36,815
What's wrong? Is something wrong?

854
01:03:36,930 --> 01:03:39,845
This is unlike you.

855
01:03:41,601 --> 01:03:45,530
Listen carefully to what I'm about to say,

856
01:03:45,538 --> 01:03:48,955
and answer me honestly.

857
01:03:50,210 --> 01:03:53,410
Why are you getting so serious? You're scaring me.

858
01:03:53,413 --> 01:03:56,440
Something really must be wrong.

859
01:03:56,449 --> 01:03:59,205
What is it?

860
01:03:59,919 --> 01:04:02,180
While you were working at the school,

861
01:04:02,188 --> 01:04:03,950
were you instructed...

862
01:04:03,957 --> 01:04:06,590
to manipulate a student record or to give awards...

863
01:04:06,593 --> 01:04:08,615
or other recognition to certain students?

864
01:04:14,367 --> 01:04:18,055
Please be honest with me. This is important.

865
01:04:19,873 --> 01:04:21,455
Well...

866
01:04:24,110 --> 01:04:28,165
I don't know about manipulating them, but isn't giving awards...

867
01:04:28,248 --> 01:04:30,705
to designated students a common practice?

868
01:04:30,717 --> 01:04:34,980
I'm a music teacher, so I need to look after the music students.

869
01:04:34,988 --> 01:04:37,550
We have a few at our school...

870
01:04:37,557 --> 01:04:39,875
Kids like Tae Ra.

871
01:04:41,127 --> 01:04:44,490
Those awards were crucial for the kids to get into good colleges.

872
01:04:44,497 --> 01:04:46,545
We had no choice.

873
01:04:46,900 --> 01:04:50,355
Only school awards can be put in the student record.

874
01:04:50,536 --> 01:04:53,755
But why are you asking that all of a sudden?

875
01:04:54,207 --> 01:04:57,770
The prosecutors will investigate our school soon.

876
01:04:57,777 --> 01:05:01,340
Investigate? The prosecutors?

877
01:05:01,347 --> 01:05:05,010
All we did was make up a few awards. Is that really necessary?

878
01:05:05,018 --> 01:05:06,650
General Manager Lee...

879
01:05:06,653 --> 01:05:08,320
tampered with Tae Ra's student record...

880
01:05:08,321 --> 01:05:10,290
to fund the takeover of the university.

881
01:05:10,290 --> 01:05:13,875
He also handed out awards exclusively to the Veritas kids.

882
01:05:14,027 --> 01:05:15,520
When the investigation starts,

883
01:05:15,528 --> 01:05:19,845
his other wrongdoings will be discovered as well.

884
01:05:20,667 --> 01:05:24,455
My goodness. The whole school will be in chaos.

885
01:05:24,537 --> 01:05:27,225
And the parents will go crazy.

886
01:05:28,408 --> 01:05:29,900
Probably.

887
01:05:29,909 --> 01:05:33,595
But this might be our chance.

888
01:05:34,681 --> 01:05:36,465
Chance?

889
01:05:36,649 --> 01:05:39,250
Our chance to solve the problems...

890
01:05:39,252 --> 01:05:41,535
that we have been ignoring...

891
01:05:41,788 --> 01:05:45,745
and give the school back to our students.

892
01:06:20,259 --> 01:06:22,160
- Gosh. - Mu Hyeok.

893
01:06:22,161 --> 01:06:24,015
Are you sure no one is here?

894
01:06:25,031 --> 01:06:26,930
All the lights are off.

895
01:06:26,933 --> 01:06:28,360
Today was the last exam day,

896
01:06:28,368 --> 01:06:30,015
so everyone has left. Come.

897
01:06:53,059 --> 01:06:55,445
What are you doing? Come on.

898
01:07:28,928 --> 01:07:30,545
Gosh.

899
01:07:31,497 --> 01:07:32,990
What? What's wrong?

900
01:07:32,999 --> 01:07:34,555
Hold on.

901
01:07:34,567 --> 01:07:36,055
What is it?

902
01:07:41,908 --> 01:07:43,395
What?

903
01:07:59,459 --> 01:08:01,045
Lee Tae Seok?

904
01:08:11,337 --> 01:08:14,355
(Class of Lies / Mr. Temporary)

905
01:08:29,288 --> 01:08:32,150
Someone murdered Lee Tae Seok and disguised it as suicide.

906
01:08:32,158 --> 01:08:33,290
That's neat.

907
01:08:33,292 --> 01:08:36,520
At this rate, the investigation will be wrapped up in no time.

908
01:08:36,529 --> 01:08:38,590
We have concluded that Mr. Lee committed suicide.

909
01:08:38,598 --> 01:08:41,255
The investigation will be terminated here.

910
01:08:41,801 --> 01:08:44,330
You're working on another Cheonmyung High School case.

911
01:08:44,337 --> 01:08:46,230
Someone died this time too.

912
01:08:46,239 --> 01:08:48,340
I hope this won't affect us.

913
01:08:48,341 --> 01:08:50,725
How dare you talk that way about my dad?

914
01:08:51,110 --> 01:08:54,240
Why did you hide it? Does that lawyer have something on you?

915
01:08:54,247 --> 01:08:56,140
I trust Beom Jin more than I trust anyone else.

916
01:08:56,149 --> 01:08:58,410
That proves how oblivious you are.

917
01:08:58,417 --> 01:08:59,910
Could Beom Jin...

918
01:08:59,919 --> 01:09:02,580
Who did he do that to?

919
01:09:02,588 --> 01:09:06,550
Everyone who was bullying me has disappeared from the school now.

920
01:09:06,559 --> 01:09:09,815
He must have wanted to keep his mouth shut by all means.

921
01:09:09,929 --> 01:09:12,945
You don't have to say anything. Anything at all.
